## GAP 7 — POM RE-DIFF NOT DONE BEFORE ITERATION 2+

### What is wrong
In iteration 2+, `vulns.json` is fresh but the tool re-attempts artifacts
the POM already has patched from iteration 1, producing zero new decisions.

